OL,5, Russia has designated Boris Akunin, one
OL,6, of the country's most popular          
OL,7, novelists, a foreign agent.            
OL,9,FMr Akunin was added to a register of   
OL,10,F"terrorists and extremists" by Russia's
OL,11,Fjustice ministry over his objections to
OL,12,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.          
OL,14,FThe 67-year-old is well-known for his  
OL,15,Flongstanding criticism of President    
OL,16,FVladimir Putin.                        
OL,18,FPrior to the war, Mr Akunin's detective
OL,19,Fnovels were best-sellers in Russia,    
OL,20,Funtil authorities banned his books.    
